M|Chec|**Be|Process-oriented tasks, quick wins, implementation help
M|Chec|**St|
M|Chec|- Ti|"[Number]-Point [Topic] Checklist"
M|Chec|it|Numbered or checkbox items
M|Chec|it|Group into logical sections if 10+ items
M|Chec|it|Brief explanation per item (1-2 sentences)
M|Chec|**Gu|
M|Chec|it|Keep to 1-2 pages
M|Chec|it|Use actionable language ("Verify X", "Set up Y", "Remove Z")
M|Chec|it|Order by workflow sequence or priority
M|Chec|it|Make it printable — clean layout, generous spacing
M|Chec|it|Include a "done" checkbox for each item
