M|Chea|it|Dense but scannable
M|Chea|it|Visual hierarchy w/ headers and grouping
M|Chea|**Gu|
M|Chea|it|op for quick reference, not reading
M|Chea|it|Use tables, grids, or columns
M|Chea|it|Include formulas, shortcuts, or code snippets
M|Chea|it|ds for printing or saving as desktop reference
M|Chea|it|Bold the most important items
